<v-card :class="'login-dialog elevation-5 ' + (isError?'shake':'')">
    <v-card-media class="login-dialog-image" :src="adminPanelImageUrl" height="120px"/>
    <v-card-text>
        <form role="login" v-on:submit.prevent="onSubmit">
            <v-text-field v-validate="{ required: true}"
                          :error-messages="errors.collect('email')"
                          name="email"
                          type="email"
                          label="Username or E-Mail"
                          v-model="form.username"/>
            <v-text-field v-validate="{ required: true}"
                          :error-messages="errors.collect('password')"
                          name="password"
                          label="Password"
                          type="password"
                          v-model="form.password"/>
            <v-btn :loading="loggingIn"
                   :disabled="errors.any() || loggingIn"
                   type="submit"
                   block
                   color="primary"
            >
                LOGIN
            </v-btn>
        </form>
    </v-card-text>
</v-card>
